Privacy Policy

This privacy policy applies to the "Health Assistant" mobile application developed by [Your Company Name].

Information We Collect

We collect the following information to provide you with health management services:

Account information you provide when registering, such as your name, email address, height, weight, gender, and date of birth.
Health and fitness information you add manually or via syncing with wearable devices, such as exercise routines, heart rate, sleep patterns, and diet logs.
Location information if you enable GPS tracking for outdoor activities.
How We Use Information

The information we collect allows us to analyze your fitness levels and habits to provide customized health and training advice. We do not share your personal information with any third parties without your consent.

Data Storage and Security

Information is stored locally on your device. We use industry-standard security measures to protect the loss, misuse, and alteration of any user data under our control.

Changes to This Policy

We may occasionally update this policy as required by law or to comply with regulations. We will notify you of any significant changes.

Contact Us

If you have any questions about this privacy policy or the handling of your personal information, please contact us at [smartisan2023@gmail.com].

